dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "Miliaria geometrica" and "Miliaria gallica".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, cities along coasts, places of historical interest.
Illustrations of sea creatures, ships, and compass roses.
Features 2 decorative cartouches with illustrations of men and cherubs.
Title given in Latin and Dutch.
